## 重要数据结构描述
ScrapeManager 是管理所有抓取的一个抽象
```
type Manager struct {
	logger    log.Logger
	append    Appendable
	graceShut chan struct{}

	jitterSeed    uint64     // Global jitterSeed seed is used to spread scrape workload across HA setup.
	mtxScrape     sync.Mutex // Guards the fields below.
