var tz map[string]int
var ds string = "abc"
// delete(map, key)
delete(tz, ds)
```

## <a id="Append"><span class="secondtitle">Append</span></a>

Append 可以接受多个参数
```
func append(slice []T, elements ...T) []T

// use case 
x := []int{1,2,3}
x = append(x, 4, 5, 6)
fmt.Println(x)
```

